- Pharmaceutical division grew 12% YoY despite patent cliff on lead product [citation]
- Medical devices segment faces 15% pricing pressure from payer negotiations [citation]
- Consumer health divestiture reduced revenue volatility by 8% in Q2 2024 [citation]
- Operating margin expanded 2.3 percentage points through cost optimization [citation]

